reviewText:
A gem of a game, not what I expected at all. It has innovative gameplay, an original storyline, and damn detailed side quest gameplay (also if you have a decent rig to play this on...well the graphics and effects are top shelf). In the end if you like crime solving games with a splash of supernatural... this game is well worth it. I highly recomend it indeed.


-Side Note (metascore);

-For the first time I really question the metascore, critics reviewing this baffle me... the users reviews are a bit more on par and fairer in their assessment... I guess in the end just watch some let's plays and see what your close friends think of it and thats that.
